[DCTF Quals 2018] Broken TV

Posted Sep 29, 2018
By Lucian Nitescu 8 min read

Description:

Guys, I’ve asked Google for this flag! But my only monitor is this Broken TV… Target: https://broken-tv.dctfq18.def.camp/

Author:

Lucian Nitescu

Stats:

83 point / 73 solvers

Solution:

The challenge started with this simple website:

We can observe that the following image is changed at about 1 minute:

Using the following Python script we can extract only the scren image with the shifted pixels.

cropped.save("e.png")

Result:

Knowing this is an identifiable Google search we can use the whitespace in order to guide our line shifting. Using OCR, I was able to decode the image and obtain the flag.
